This Folder is a collection of Internet of Things (IoT) projects built primarily with the ESP32 platform.
It includes hands-on experiments, prototypes, and demos that explore embedded systems, real-time applications, and interactive devices.

Projects in this folder :

🕹️ Fun applications like mini-games (e.g., Chrome Dino Game on TFT & OLED).

📡 IoT connectivity experiments with sensors and actuators.

⚡ Hardware-software integration using PlatformIO and the Arduino framework.
